\# Health Tracker Pro ðŸ’œ



A full-stack health monitoring application with BMI, WHR, and Heart Rate calculators.



\## Features

\- BMI Calculator

\- Waist-to-Hip Ratio (WHR) Calculator

\- Heart Rate Analysis

\- Personalized Health Recommendations



\## Tech Stack

\- Frontend: React.js, Tailwind CSS

\- Backend: Node.js, Express

\- Containerization: Docker



\## Run Locally



\### Without Docker

```bash

\# Frontend

cd frontend

npm install

npm start



\# Backend

cd backend

npm install

npm start

```



\### With Docker

```bash

docker-compose up --build

```



\## Access

\- Frontend: http://localhost:3000

\- Backend: http://localhost:5000

